snippet.title: Mario Rainbow Castle + Luigi Engine Room in Mario Party Superstars mod!
snippet.description:
Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/419979

Credits
Mario's Rainbow Castle
Lead of project - Sebzouy (https://twitter.com/Sebzouy)
Modeler and Logo art - justcamtro
Modeler - Tenacious
Map - joshthegamer
Remixed soundtracks - JustRyland (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JCfMs-JGLOg&t=0s&ab_channel=JustRylandMusic)


Luigi's Engine Room
Lead of project - Sebzouy (https://twitter.com/Sebzouy)
Modeler - Alkaline6022 (https://www.artstation.com/alkaline)
Map - joshthegamer
Logo art - justcamtro
Remixed soundtracks - JustRyland (https://www.youtube.com/@JustRylandMusic)

This trailer was also featured in the latest Nintendo Fan-Games Direct! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dPRaePoZN50
